        "column_K8gfik": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Fix_problems_in_real_time_icon_bf459b4a-2417-41ca-b9db-5169a480831a.svg",
            "title": "<strong>Fix problems in real time</strong>",
            "text": "<p>When clients take the survey we can provide immediate results. Customer service may be lagging or wait times are too long. Whatever the problem, you must take quick action to maintain guest satisfaction. ExperienceStream delivers alerts directly to your phone – allowing you to address issues right away.</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "is_card_clickable": false
          }
        },
        "column_RKKUqR": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Engage_staff_icon_827ed590-3bb0-43e3-b3a7-6209dda25a59.svg",
            "title": "<strong>Engage staff</strong>",
            "text": "<p>Employee turnover is a serious concern in the spa sector and increases costs for hiring and training. As well, managers must work hard to reward and encourage employees.</p><p>With ExperienceStream, clients can provide specific feedback about the staff who served them. Positive comments let you thank and recognize team members. Poor results give you a heads up to coach staff to improve their customer service.</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "is_card_clickable": false
          }
        },
        "column_nQXpRz": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Avoid_nasty_reviews_icon_90d7bf13-207e-4b75-9e3a-831f958efc53.svg",
            "title": "<strong>Avoid nasty reviews</strong>",
            "text": "<p>Like many service industries, spas rely on favourable posts on social media to gain new customers. However, sometimes things go wrong.</p><p>When a client gives a negative evaluation at a kiosk, the ExperienceStream system can automatically generate a coupon for them. As the spa manager, you control the coupon offers – such as a discount on a future visit or special prices on products.</p><p><strong>When the client leaves your spa, they will be feeling more positive and may drop the idea of posting a negative review.</strong></p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "is_card_clickable": false
          }
        },
        "column_whJT6V": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Generate_revenue_icon_59411f62-e8df-472e-ad83-f928e6763b64.svg",
            "title": "<strong>Generate revenue</strong>",
            "text": "<p>Every spa wants to increase its sales per customer. ExperienceStream can print coupons for survey respondents, offering a discount on additional products and services.</p><p><strong>Gather data and increase revenue at the same time!</strong></p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "is_card_clickable": false
          }
        }
      },
